    "Consistency assessments and representative participant responses for each category are showcased in the following sub-sections.",
    "When asked about the ideal L2 self, a consensus emerged among participants, with all expressing an aspiration to become more proficient or professional English users.",
    "Participant B, for instance, said: \"I think it is important to become fluent in English…Being a fluent English speaker is the main reason why I chose to study the English major\".",
    "This may reflect their awareness of their ideal L2 selves and the motivation derived from their aspiration to become proficient English speakers.",
    "Hence, the qualitative data for this category aligns with the high mean values in the quantitative data."
